body:
`geoWithin` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
  "$search": {
     "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
     "geoWithin": {
        "path": "<field-to-search>",
        "box | circle | geometry": <object>,
        "score": <score-options>
     }
  }
}
```

